{"tid":736183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE出道以來最大尺度！　MOMO深V挖洞泳裝超性感","createTime":"2018-07-10T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:09:09.000Z","uid":51412,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"50d0cd3011d108fb4584a4e59ae6dbd9a1b4b448","tid":736183,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"韓團TWICE將在9日以新曲《Dance The Night Away》回歸，午間時先公佈了每次宣傳期都有的TWICE TV第一集，讓粉絲們搶先看這次的服裝造型，隊長志效害羞地說：「第一次穿露這麼多的衣服，也是第一次全員都穿無袖。」一轉身就可以看見她露出整片美背，其他成員的造型也都讓人眼睛一亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3394/d3394915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3394%2Fd3394915.jpg&h=90e14fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE出道以來多走清新甜美路線，這次回歸挑戰大尺度，全員穿上泳衣露出美背、小蠻腰外還有隱藏的事業線，就如在大夏天回歸般的火辣，在9日搶先公開的《TWICE TV：Dance The Night Away》第一集中，可以看見娜璉穿著腰兩邊都被挖空的性感泳裝，談話期間彎腰時不小心就露出隱藏的好身材。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3404/d3404118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3404%2Fd3404118.jpg&h=4ad4b5f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉好身材。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n而以跳舞實力和好身材出名的MOMO自然也不遑多讓，以胸前的蝴蝶結作為重點，上下挖空露出性感深溝，多賢、志效、彩瑛則是整個被挖空，子瑜、Mina、Sana、定延則以細肩帶或小可愛露出香肩，每個人都展顯了屬於自己的小女人味。其中特別的是，定延在演唱會時有接髮以長髮造型現身，發現粉絲們都很喜歡的樣子，所以這次回歸又再次接髮增添女人味，十分漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3404/d3404117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3404%2Fd3404117.jpg&h=93f4a758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMO穿上深V露肚泳衣也相當有自信。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3404/d3404116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3404%2Fd3404116.jpg&h=5f5ea7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲定延接髮。（圖／翻攝自TWICE VLIVE）"},{"pid":"ad8f3c08785a5d2271e80f3b8bdd15cef3bb030a","tid":736183,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好丁"},{"pid":"2df89fd3ff4560de71172db1b58b81306f501f43","tid":736183,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc56624533d62844b00b2555db6e1e4c71e882eb","tid":736183,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6b75593b849f78103b9820c847b93721b7ed17c","tid":736183,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f197f5f5ea32cc84f39bc698235442b9fdf6813","tid":736183,"uid":104308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"開始賣肉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adda3e0bc8a4620956c74d1e67006e84a86e3645","tid":736183,"uid":16326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"兒童色情"},{"pid":"8305bd155d42e4b06f2039aeb1192f9a3661a1e8","tid":736183,"uid":19264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"Momo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21b9529bf1323726863422d7769dcac11184cf","tid":736183,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"長髮唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a8ec9a9dd4f2338b427591cd451a2b2c092ba5","tid":736183,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb7f713319035bfeb42589813c21d09ce0a1013","tid":736183,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"閪女人好似有d波路 幾正"},{"pid":"b9da1cc92eeb78a01ac006422175fce3dc96557